# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root .env — OPTIONAL now.
#
# docker-compose.yml is GENERATED from config/models.json by
#   uv run --with pyyaml python infra/scripts/generate-compose.py
# with llama.cpp args (model_file, model_url, ctx_size, threads, parallel,
# threads_http) baked in as literals from the registry — so this file is no
# longer needed to tune the model containers. Edit config/models.json instead.
#
# Kept only as a place for ad-hoc shell/env overrides if you add ${VAR} refs to
# the compose generator yourself.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
